Home > Music > Migos Performed "Emmitt Smith" For Emmitt Smith In Houston Migos Performed "Emmitt Smith" For Emmitt Smith In Houston 0 0 Posted by Devon Jefferson , Feb 7, 2017 at 08:02pm Emmitt Smith went crazy when the Migos performed "Emmitt Smith." 
The Migos had an eventful Superbowl weekend as their hometown team took on the Patriots. Even though the Falcons lost and Offset lost $50,000 because of it, the trio appears to have enjoyed themselves in Houston for Superbowl LI. 
One of the highlights of their weekend was the encounter they had with the legendary NFL player Emmitt Smith. Quavo posted a picture to his Instagram of the group holding up jerseys next to smith earlier in the weekend, but it looks like that wasn't the only time the Migos and Smith linked up in Houston. 
According to a report from TMZ , the Migos performed at a New Era event that running back was in attendance for. In the video below you can see Smith get super turnt when the Migos performed their track "Emmitt Smith." Dude even hits a mean dab with his drink still in hand as the rappers turned up on stage.
